{"title": "Josafat", "description": "En Josafat \u00e9s el campaner de l\u2019esgl\u00e9sia de Santa Maria. Al principi, feia companyia a un vell parroqui\u00e0, per\u00f2 despr\u00e9s de la seva mort exerceix sol amb el vistiplau de l'Esgl\u00e9sia. A trav\u00e9s d'un vell conegut, entra en relaci\u00f3 amb dues prostitutes que el portaran a una aventura sexual de dif\u00edcil de conciliar amb les convencions socials i amb la seva consci\u00e8ncia.<br><br>\r\n\r\nJosafat is the bell-ringer of St. Mary's Church. At first, he kept company with an old parishioner, but after his death he stays alone with the approval of the Church. Through an old acquaintance, he comes into contact with two prostitutes who will take him on a sexual adventure that is difficult to reconcile with social conventions and with his own conscience.\r\n - Summary by Joan Pujolar", "duration": 8785, "language": "Catalan", "authors": [{"id": "16629", "name": "Prudenci Bertrana"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/josafat_2209_librivox/josafat_2210.jpg", "copyright_year": "1906", "genres": ["Literary Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "jpujolar"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Kazbek"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Francesc"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Cap\u00edtol 1", "readers": [17572], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/josafat_2209_librivox/josafat_1_bertrana_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1393}, {"section": 2, "title": "Cap\u00edtol 2", "readers": [17595], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/josafat_2209_librivox/josafat_2_bertrana_64kb.mp3", "duration": 214}, {"section": 3, "title": "Cap\u00edtol 3", "readers": [17650], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/josafat_2209_librivox/josafat_3_bertrana_64kb.mp3", "duration": 857}, {"section": 4, "title": "Cap\u00edtol 4", "readers": [17720], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/josafat_2209_librivox/josafat_4_bertrana